He sits at the long table, says little, and the quality of the arguments improves noticeably, because nobody wants to say something stupid in front of Campa.

@campa_internacional
title: El viejo bolchevique
subtitle: His authority steadies the orthodox and manages the Moscow question the way only a man jailed for the cause can.
card-image: img/portraits/campa.jpg
choose-if: advisor_action_timer == 0
unavailable-subtitle: [? if advisor_action_timer > 0 : [+ advisor_action_timer +] months before next advisor action. ?]
on-arrival: advisor_action_timer = 6; last_advisor_action = 1; political_capital += 3; unity += 3; des_ortodoxos -= 8; moscow_relation += 3; fac_ortodoxos += 2

When Campa speaks about discipline, the orthodox listen, because he paid for the right in eleven years of Lecumberri and never once asked for the receipt. The corriente that most wants Moscow respected is calmed by the one man who can criticize Moscow without being called a traitor. The family stays at one table a while longer, which in this Party is a full-time job.
